
tests::::

// base_test:
// - Common UVM test that:
//   * Fetches driver and monitor virtual interfaces (vif_drv, vif_mon).
//   * Passes them via config_db to env.agt.drv, env.agt.mon, and env.cov.
//   * Creates the uart_env instance.
// - All specific tests (smoke/back_to_back/gap/random) extend this.


// smoke_test:
// - Extends base_test.
// - Runs uart_smoke_seq on env.agt.sqr.
// - Purpose: basic connectivity / sanity check with a few fixed bytes.


// back_to_back_test:
// - Extends base_test.
// - Runs uart_back_to_back_seq on env.agt.sqr.
// - Purpose: stress continuous TX/RX with no idle gaps between frames.


// gap_test:
// - Extends base_test.
// - Runs uart_gap_seq on env.agt.sqr.
// - Purpose: exercise UART under random idle gaps between frames.


// random_test:
// - Extends base_test.
// - Runs uart_random_seq on env.agt.sqr.
// - Purpose: long random regression to catch rare timing and data issues.
